{"tid":1759914,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北角男子墮樓亡 斷肢跌入低層平台","createTime":"2019-11-28T01:35:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T02:38:16.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fcee497dca75f4b27f42833832402a9d2d2a3da1","tid":1759914,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:35:50.000Z","msg":"北角清晨有人從高處墮下，當場死亡，有斷肢跌入一單位平台，住客大驚。<br />\n<br />\n現場是北角英皇道52至56號，清晨5時50分，一名男子由高處墮下，期間撞向石屎簷篷，撞斷一隻腳，殘肢跌入低層一個單位的平台。警員及救護員到場，證實47歲姓蕭男子已傷重死亡，正調查男子墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191128/_2019112809280724647.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191128%2F_2019112809280724647.jpg&h=921ae266&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1648240/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%94%B7%E5%AD%90%E5%A2%AE%E6%A8%93%E4%BA%A1-%E6%96%B7%E8%82%A2%E8%B7%8C%E5%85%A5%E4%BD%8E%E5%B1%A4%E5%B9%B3%E5%8F%B0%E4%BD%8F%E5%AE%A2%E5%A4%A7%E9%A9%9A</code></pre>"},{"pid":"808ea382f762c0e04878e5ed2891bc160bea147d","tid":1759914,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:36:43.000Z","msg":"正調查男子墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n即係唔係被自殺"},{"pid":"05297750c7a1848b00204cc7f5c7148d1a2b4843","tid":1759914,"uid":298054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"808ea382f762c0e04878e5ed2891bc160bea147d","tid":1759914,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:36:43.000Z","msg":"正調查男子墮樓原因。<br />\n<br />\n即係唔係被自殺"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:42:53.000Z","msg":"之後咪又變事件冇可疑"},{"pid":"919c4f7967f36c15c2db06369bc88ed0aa509826","tid":1759914,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"808ea382f762c0e04878e5ed2891bc160bea147d","tid":1759914,"uid":20222,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:36:43.000Z","msg":"正調查男子墮樓原因。<br